rComments: Explications toujours claires, vraiment gentil, prend le temps d'expliquer et de réexpliquer chaque notion si on ne comprend pas. Cet homme est un génie! Really funny prof, good sense of humour and learned all of our names so he could address us properly. I don't like physics but I was surprised when a 3 hour class went by fast. Recommended.
